# One of the Ninety-and-Nine

What does the Father and the Savior have to do with the Ninety-and-Nine, those who aren't rebellious and seeking to leave? 

* He loves all of His sheep. He wants to connect with, love, and be close to His sheep. The lost as well as the ninety-and-nine.

